{"kanda":6,"sarga":82,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"श्रुत्वातुभीमनिर्ह्रादंशक्राशनिसमस्वनम् ।वीक्षमाणादिशस्सर्वादुद्रुवुर्वानरर्षभा:","trans":"The bulls among Vanaras heard the roar which was like thunder and looking at Indrajith fled in all directions.","words":[{"d":"शक्राशनिसमस्वनम्","m":"whose roar was like thunder"},{"d":"भीमनिर्ह्रादम्","m":"terrible roar"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"वानरर्षभा","m":"bulls among Vanaras"},{"d":"वीक्षमाणाः","m":"looking at"},{"d":"सर्वाः","m":"all"},{"d":"दिशः","m":"directions"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"at speed"},{"d":"दुद्रुवुः","m":"fled"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"तानुवाचततःसर्वान्हनुमान् मारुतात्मजः ।विषण्णवदनान्दीनांस्त्रस्तान्विद्रवतःपृथक्","trans":"Thereafter, Maruti's son, Hanuman said to all Vanaras who were looking sad, piteous, feeling singly out of fear, and running away.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"मारुतात्मजः","m":"Maruti's son"},{"d":"हनुमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"विषण्णवदनान्","m":"sad face"},{"d":"दीनान्","m":"piteous"},{"d":"त्रस्तान्","m":"in fear"},{"d":"पृथक्","m":"separately"},{"d":"विद्रवतः","m":"running away"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"to all"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"said"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"कस्माद्विषण्णवदनाविद्रवध्वंप्लवङ्गमाः ।त्यक्तयुद्धसमुत्साहाश्शूरत्वंक्वनुवोगतम्","trans":"\"O monkeys! Why have you lost enthusiasm to fight, looking sad and running away? Where has your valour gone?\"","words":[{"d":"प्लवङ्गमाः","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"त्यक्तयुद्धसमुत्साहाः","m":"lost enthusiasm to fight"},{"d":"कस्मात्","m":"why"},{"d":"विद्रवध्वे","m":"running away"},{"d":"वः","m":"or"},{"d":"शूरत्वम्","m":"valour"},{"d":"क्व","m":"where"},{"d":"गतम्","m":"has it gone"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"पृष्ठतोऽनुव्रजध्वंमामग्रतोयन्तमाहवे ।शूरैरनिजनोपेतैरयुक्तंहिनिवर्तितुम्","trans":"\"Return and come in front, close to me and follow me. It is not proper for you to win wars and be praised.\"","words":[{"d":"आहवे","m":"return"},{"d":"यान्तम्","m":"close to"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"अनुव्रजध्वम्","m":"who won wars"},{"d":"अभिजनोपेतैः","m":"who were praised"},{"d":"शूरैः","m":"heroes"},{"d":"निवर्तितुम्","m":"returning"},{"d":"अयुक्तंहि","m":"not proper"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"एवमुक्तास्सुसङ्क्रुद्धावायुपुत्रेणधीमता ।शैलशृङ्गान् द्रुमांश्चवजगृहुर्हृष्टमानसाः","trans":"Wise son of wind god having spoken in that way, delighted in mind the Vanaras seized peaks of mountains and also trees in great fury.","words":[{"d":"धीमता","m":"wise"},{"d":"वायुपुत्रेण","m":"by Son of windgod"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्ताः","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"हृष्टमानसाः","m":"delighted in mind"},{"d":"सुसङ्क्रुद्धाः","m":"great fury"},{"d":"शैलशृङ्गान्","m":"peak of mountain"},{"d":"द्रुमान् चैव","m":"and also trees"},{"d":"जगृहुः","m":"seized"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"अभिपेतुश्चगर्जन्तोराक्षसान्वानरर्षभाः ।परिवार्यहनूमन्तमन्वयुश्चमहाहवे","trans":"Surrounding Hanuman, the Vanara leaders followed him for a great fight.","words":[{"d":"वानरर्षभाः","m":"bull among Vanaras"},{"d":"गर्जन्तः","m":"roaring"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"अभिपेतुः","m":"surrounding"},{"d":"महाहवे","m":"in great fight"},{"d":"हनूमन्तम्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"परिवार्य","m":"Vanara leaders"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"स तैर्वानरमुख्यैश्चहनुमान्सर्वतोवृतः ।हुताशनइवार्चिष्मानदहच्छत्रुवाहिनीम्","trans":"Hanuman went surrounded by Vanara leaders who resembled flaming fire and began to consume the enemy troops like flaming fire.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"हनुमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"तैः","m":"those"},{"d":"वानरमुख्यैः","m":"Vanara leaders"},{"d":"सर्वतंवृतः","m":"surrounded all over"},{"d":"हुताशनःइव","m":"like flaming fire"},{"d":"शत्रुवाहिनीम्","m":"enemy troops"},{"d":"अदहत्","m":"consumed"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"स राक्षसानांकदनंचकारसुमहाकपिः ।वृतोवानरसैन्येनकालान्तकयोमोपमः","trans":"The Vanara army surrounded that great monkey, Hanuman, who was like Yama, the god of death and caused havoc to Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"वानरसैन्येन","m":"Vanara army"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded"},{"d":"सःमहाकपिः","m":"that great monkey"},{"d":"कालान्तकयमोपमः","m":"like Yama the spirit of death"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"कदनम्","m":"havoc"},{"d":"चक्रे","m":"caused"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"स तुकोपेनचाविष्टःशोकेन च महाकपिः ।हनूमान्रावणिरथेमहतींपातयच्छिलाम्","trans":"Hanuman, overtaken by anger, filled with great sorrow hurled a huge rock at the chariot of Ravana's son.","words":[{"d":"महता","m":"great"},{"d":"शोकेन","m":"sorrow"},{"d":"कोपेन च","m":"angry"},{"d":"अविष्टः","m":"overtaken"},{"d":"महाकपिः","m":"greatVanara"},{"d":"सःहनुमान्","m":"that Hanuman"},{"d":"रावणिरथे","m":"on the chariot of the son of Ravana"},{"d":"महतीम्","m":"huge"},{"d":"शिलाम्","m":"rock"},{"d":"पातयत्","m":"hurled"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"तामापतन्तींदृष्टवैवरथस्सारथिनातदा ।विधेयाश्वसमायुक्तोविदूरमपवाहितः","trans":"Then seeing that rock coming towards the chariot yoked to obedient horses, the chariot rider drove it to a long distance.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"अपततनीम्","m":"fallen"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"that"},{"d":"दृष्टवैव","m":"seeing"},{"d":"विधेयाश्वसमायुक्तः","m":"yoked to obedient horses"},{"d":"सारथिना","m":"chariot rider"},{"d":"विदूरम्","m":"long distance"},{"d":"अपवाहितः","m":"drove"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"तमिन्द्रजितमप्राप्यरथस्थंसहसारथिम् ।विवेशधरणींभित्त्वासाशिलाव्यर्थमुद्यता","trans":"That rock hurled by Hanuman failed to reach the chariot in which Indrajith was seated and also the charioteer. It cleaved the earth and entered.","words":[{"d":"व्यर्थम्","m":"failed"},{"d":"उद्यत","m":"raised up"},{"d":"साशिला","m":"that rock"},{"d":"रथस्थम्","m":"to the chariot"},{"d":"सहसारथिम्","m":"along with charioteer"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"इन्द्रजितम्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"अप्राप्य","m":"having not reached"},{"d":"धरणीम्","m":"on the earth"},{"d":"भित्त्वा","m":"cleaving"},{"d":"विवेश","m":"entered"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"पतितायांशिलायांतुव्यथितारक्षसांचमूः ।निपतन्त्या च शिलयाराक्षसामथिताभृशम्","trans":"As the rock fell on the battlefield the Rakshasa troops got alarmed and were violently crushed to death.","words":[{"d":"शिलायाम्","m":"rock"},{"d":"पतितायाम्","m":"fell"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"चमूः","m":"troops"},{"d":"व्यथितः","m":"alarmed"},{"d":"निपतन्त्या","m":"on the battlefield"},{"d":"शिलया","m":"rock"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"violently"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"तमभ्यधावन् शतशोनदन्तःकाननौकसः ।तेद्रुमांश्चमहाकायागिरिशृङ्गाणिचोद्यताः","trans":"Those gigantic forest dwellers in hundreds seizing trees and rocks lifted and fought making loud noise.","words":[{"d":"महाकायाः","m":"of gigantic body"},{"d":"तेकाननौकसः","m":"those forest dwellers"},{"d":"शतशः","m":"hundreds"},{"d":"द्रुमांश्च","m":"trees"},{"d":"गिरिशृङ्गाणि","m":"peaks of mountains च also"},{"d":"उद्यताः","m":"raised up"},{"d":"नदन्तः","m":"making loud noise"},{"d":"तम्","m":"them"},{"d":"अभ्यधावन्","m":"fought"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"क्षिपनीन्द्रजितंसङ्ख्येवानराभीमविक्रमाः ।वृक्षशैलमहावर्षंविसृजन्तःप्लवङ्गमाः शत्रूणांकदनंचक्रुर्नेदुश्चविविधैस्स्वनैः ।","trans":"Courageous Vanaras, innumerable in number began to rain trees and rocks throwing on the enemies. The Rakshasas number rolled on the battlefield shouting in numerous tones.","words":[{"d":"भीमविक्रमाः","m":"courageous"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सङ्ख्ये","m":"inumerable"},{"d":"इन्द्रजितम्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"क्षिपन्ति","m":"discharged"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गमाः","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"वृक्षशलमहावर्षम्","m":"rained trees and rocks"},{"d":"विसृजन्तः","m":"throwing"},{"d":"शत्रूणाम्","m":"enemies"},{"d":"कदनम्","m":"on the battlefield"},{"d":"विविधैः","m":"numerous"},{"d":"नेदुश्च","m":"shouting"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"वानरैसैर्महाभीमैर्घोररूपानिशाचराः वीर्यादभिहतावृक्षैर्व्यचेष्टन्तरणक्षितौ ।","trans":"Night rangers of dreadful appearance beaten up with trees by most fierce Vanaras, fell on the battlefield and struck one another.","words":[{"d":"घोररूपाः","m":"dreadful appearance"},{"d":"निशाचराः","m":"night rangers"},{"d":"महाभीमैः","m":"very fierce तैःवानरैः those Vanaras"},{"d":"वीर्यात्","m":"violently"},{"d":"वृक्षैः","m":"trees"},{"d":"अभिहताः","m":"beaten up"},{"d":"रणक्षितौ","m":"fell on battlefield"},{"d":"व्यचेष्टन्त","m":"hit one another"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"स्वसैन्यमभिवीक्ष्याथवानरार्दितमिन्द्रजित् प्रगृहीतायुधःक्रुद्धःपरानभिमुखोययौ ।","trans":"Indrajith, looking at his own army tormented by the Vanaras, was enraged, and went towards the enemies' seizing weapons.","words":[{"d":"इन्द्रजित्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"वानरार्दितम्","m":"tormented by Vanaras"},{"d":"स्वसैन्यम्","m":"his own army"},{"d":"अभिवीक्ष्य","m":"looking at"},{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"प्रगृहीतायुधः","m":"seizing weapons"},{"d":"परान्","m":"enemies"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"सःशरौघानवसृजन्स्वसैन्येनाभिसम्वृतः जघानकपिशार्दूलान्सुबहून्दृष्टविक्रमः ।","trans":"Indrajith of unyielding valour, combining with his own army let go numerous arrows on the tigers of Vanaras and struck them.","words":[{"d":"दृष्टविक्रमः","m":"unyielding valour"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"स्वसैन्येन","m":"by his own army"},{"d":"अभिसम्वृतः","m":"combined with"},{"d":"शरौघान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"अवसृजन्","m":"let go"},{"d":"सुबहून्","m":"numerous"},{"d":"कपिशार्दूलान्","m":"tigers among monkeys"},{"d":"जघान","m":"struck"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"शूलैःरशनिभिःखङ्गै: पट्टसै: कूटमुद्गरैः तेचाप्यनुचरास्तस्यवानरान्जघ्नुराहवे ।","trans":"In the battle, followers of Indrajith struck the Vanaras with tridents, asanis, swords, sharp edged spears, and kutamudgaras.","words":[{"d":"आहवे","m":"in the battle"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"ते","m":"those"},{"d":"अनुचराः","m":"followers अपि also"},{"d":"अशनिभिः","m":"Asanis"},{"d":"खङ्गै:","m":"swords"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"जघ्नुः","m":"struck"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"स्कन्धविटपैश्शालैश्शिलाभिश्चमहाबलः हनूमान्कदनंचक्रेरक्षसांभीमकर्मणाम् ।","trans":"Hanuman, who was endowed with great strength, killed Rakshasas capable of terrific tasks with trees having large trunks and branches and stones also.","words":[{"d":"महाबलः","m":"endowed with great strength"},{"d":"हनूमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"सस्कन्धविटपैः","m":"trees with huge trunks and branches"},{"d":"शिलाभिश्च","m":"stones also"},{"d":"भीमकर्मणाम्","m":"of terrific task"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"कदनम्","m":"war"},{"d":"चक्रे","m":"killed"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"सनिवार्यपरानीकमब्रवीत्तान्वनौकसः हनूमान् सन्निवर्तध्वं न नस्साध्यमिदंबलम् ।","trans":"Hanuman made the enemy army retreat, and spoke to his own army,\" No use of defeating this army for us as our mission is not winning the army.\"","words":[{"d":"सःहनूमान्","m":"that Hanuman"},{"d":"परानीकम्","m":"enemy army"},{"d":"निवार्य","m":"retreat"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"सन्निवर्तध्वम्","m":"no use defeating this army"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"नः","m":"not"},{"d":"साध्यम्","m":"possible"},{"d":"न","m":"not"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"त्यक्त्वाप्राणान्विवेष्टन्तोरामप्रियचिकीर्षवः यन्निमित्तंहियुध्यामोहतासाजनकात्मजा ।","trans":"\"To please Rama, we are giving up life. Let us make Rama know that the daughter of Janaka for whose sake we are fighting this war and giving up life has been killed.\"","words":[{"d":"रामप्रियचिकीर्षवः","m":"What is pleasing to Rama"},{"d":"प्राणान्","m":"life"},{"d":"त्यक्त्वा","m":"giving up"},{"d":"युध्यामः","m":"war"},{"d":"साजनकात्मजा","m":"that daughter of Janak"},{"d":"हता","m":"has been killed"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"इममर्थंहिविज्ञाप्यरामंसुग्रीवमेव च तौयत्प्रतिविधास्येतेतत्करिष्यामहेवयम् ।","trans":"\"On telling this fact (that Indrajith has killed Sita) to Rama and Sugriva and knowing their reply we will do what is to be done.\"","words":[{"d":"इमम्","m":"this"},{"d":"अर्थम्","m":"fact"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"to Rama"},{"d":"सुग्रीवमेव च","m":"and Sugriva"},{"d":"विज्ञाप्य","m":"telling"},{"d":"तौ","m":"both"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"प्रतिविधास्येते","m":"knowing their reply"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"वयम्","m":"we"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"त्युक्त्वावानरश्रेष्ठोवारयन्सर्ववानरान् शनैश्शनैरसन्त्रस्तस्सबलस्सन्यवर्तत ।","trans":"The foremost of the Vanaras, kept back all the Vanaras after speaking that way to the army and slowly and slowly retreated.","words":[{"d":"वानरश्रेष्ठः","m":"foremost of Vanaras"},{"d":"सर्ववानारन्","m":"all Vanaras"},{"d":"वारयन्","m":"keeping back"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"spoken"},{"d":"सबलः","m":"his army"},{"d":"संन्यवर्तत","m":"retreated"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"ततःप्रेक्ष्यहनूमन्तंव्रजन्तंयत्रराघवः स होतुकामोदुष्टात्मागतश्चैत्यंनिकुम्भिलाम् ।","trans":"Thereafter, observing Hanuman going to Raghava, the evil minded Indrajith went to Nikumbhilam desiring to offer oblations at the sanctuary.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"दुष्टात्मा","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"यत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"व्रजन्तम्","m":"sanctuary"},{"d":"हनूमन्तं","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"प्रेक्ष्य","m":"observing"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलाम्","m":"Nikumbhila"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"निकुम्भिलामधिष्ठायपावकंजुहवेन्द्रजित् यज्ञभूम्यांततोगत्वापावकस्तेनरक्षसा ।हूयमानःप्रजज्वालमांसशोणितभुक्तदा","trans":"Indrajith reaching Nikumbhilam, the sacrificial ground, poured oblation of blood into the sacrificial fire for Devatas and the fire blazed.","words":[{"d":"इन्द्रजित्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलाम्","m":"Nikumbhilam"},{"d":"अधिष्ठाय","m":"reaching"},{"d":"पावकम्","m":"fire"},{"d":"ततः","m":"there upon"},{"d":"यज्ञभूम्याम्","m":"sacrificial ground"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"went"},{"d":"तेनरक्षसा","m":"by that Rakshasa"},{"d":"हूयमानः","m":"offering to Devatas"},{"d":"पावकः","m":"fire"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"मांसशोणितभुक्","m":"consuming blood oblations"},{"d":"प्रजज्वाल","m":"blazed"}]},{"v":26,"dev":"निकुम्भिलामधिष्ठायपावकंजुहवेन्द्रजित् यज्ञभूम्यांततोगत्वापावकस्तेनरक्षसा ।हूयमानःप्रजज्वालमांसशोणितभुक्तदा","trans":"Indrajith reaching Nikumbhilam, the sacrificial ground, poured oblation of blood into the sacrificial fire for Devatas and the fire blazed.","words":[{"d":"इन्द्रजित्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलाम्","m":"Nikumbhilam"},{"d":"अधिष्ठाय","m":"reaching"},{"d":"पावकम्","m":"fire"},{"d":"ततः","m":"there 